arbage-ShirleyManson-Getty-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px" /></p><p>由于主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shirley-manson">雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson)</a>受伤，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">垃圾乐队</a>取消了 2024 年剩余的演出。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbages-shirley-manson-interview-bleed-like-me-dave-grohl-new-album-industry-3614427">Garbage 的雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson)：“我们正在失去来自工人阶级出身和敢于冒险的乐队”</a></strong></li></ul><p>在今天（8 月 2 日）<a href="https://www.instagram.com/garbage/p/C-JKwJPSKuM/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">的 Instagram</a>帖子中，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-big-interview-nme-icon-shirley-manson-on-the-metoo-movement-dolores-oriordan-and-the-future-of-garbage-2241063"><em>NME</em>偶像奖得主</a>在他们的帐户上代表乐队分享了这条消息。他们写道，曼森的伤势“需要手术和康复来纠正”，并且这个决定并不是“轻率做出的”。</p><p> “没有人比我更对此感到沮丧。你知道，如果可以的话，我会坚持到底。”曼森在帖子的标题中写道。在声明中，乐队还明确表示他们将于 2025 年重返舞台。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C-JKwJPSKuM/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" 